{
  "stem": "5758.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we were completely degradated, degradated by the whole atmosphere.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "To go and relieve yourself in the sanitary bucket in front of everybody, It is something terribly degrading.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And [SIGHS] it was an ordeal, an ordeal that we experienced, which I will never, ever forget.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "When I saw and I saw the train, sequence of the train with Jews, I must tell you, this is something that affected me most, more than anything else.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And today-- no, I must say, I used to, used to dream a lot about this particular sequence in the train.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it was something that I don't know whether anybody can understand it who has not experienced it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't-- I can't imagine it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because the whole atmosphere was-- you become a sub-human to a certain extent.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The thoughts, why do they hit us?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We are human beings.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Why do they hit us?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Why are we-- why are we being treated just because we are Jews?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It is just unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we had these discussions during the train.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, you know, the train was nearly completely dark.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But up on top, there was a little window, which was barbed wired.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the, the relationship between the inmates of this train was not terribly a friendly one, because everybody was just caring for themselves to survive, to, to be comfortable, as comfortable as one possibly can.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And if you-- God forbid, you stepped on somebody's toe or somebody's foot or something, it, it was abuse coming from him.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The anger, and, and-- it was something really unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I feel that this is the worst thing that-- one of the worst thing that remains in my memory forever.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
